programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

programme.title: Jangan Gelak Ep01
programme.desc: Jangan Gelak dengan minggu kokurikulum di sekolah memberikan denda kepada beberapa orang murid kerana kurang berdisiplin. Di antara denda yang perlu dilakukan oleh mereka adalah: 1. denda minum air wasabi, dua orang pelajar mesti minum menggunakan straw dengan tangan diikat di belakang. 2. denda masukkan katak kecil didalam baju 3. denda pecahkan telur ayam pada dahi. 4. di akhir episod menobatkan seorang pelajar cemerlang sepanjang aktiviti kokurikulum sekolah menengah kebangsaan jangan gelak. Ammar Titan dinobatkan sebagai pelajar cemerlang pada minggu ini.

programme.title: In Person S2 Ep12

programme.title: Pembancuh Kopi Mr Vampire S1 Ep17
programme.desc: Nuzul membuat persiapan untuk ke Ipoh. Dia menyewa sebuah bilik di sana. Setiap minggu dia berjanji akan pulang melawat Nazrul, Nurin dan Nuha. Nuha berjanji akan menjaga adik-adiknya dengan baik. Safwan juga berjanji akan menjaga mereka semua. Nuzul senang hati. Dia diterima bekerja di sebuah kilang perabot. Irsyad dan Nuzul melalui fasa-fasa dalam kehidupan mereka dimana Nuzul berjanji untuk terus melupakan Irsyad dari episod hidupnya dan Irsyad berjanji akan terus menjejak Nuzul kerana itulah nadi hidupnya.

programme.title: Kandas
programme.desc: Seorang arkeologis bernama Amir dan seorang wartawan bernama Aina terjebak dalam kejar-kejaran dengan kumpulan samseng di hutan Perak setelah menemukan bangkai kapal terbang British. Selama melarikan diri, mereka menghadapi berbagai rintangan dan berangsur-angsur membangun hubungan yang erat. Di tengah petualangan itu, perasaan di antara mereka mulai berkembang, meskipun Amir masih mencintai Salina dan Aina memiliki hubungan dengan Wahid. Setelah melewati banyak cobaan, mereka berhasil keluar dari hutan. Wahid, yang telah menerima kenyataan kehilangan Aina, memutuskan untuk becuti di luar negara. Di saat yang sama, hubungan antara Salina dan Amir terus berkembang.

programme.desc: Suatu hari, Aisyah telah mengejutkan ZAHLIA BAHAWA dia akan berkahwin dengan Danny .Zahlia mula rasa tidak sedap hati dan merasakan Danny sebenarnya cuba ambil kesempatan ke atas Aisyah. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep01
programme.desc: Nizam (Angah) dan Mizan (Along) dua beradik dari satu keluarga. Nizam lulusan luar negeri, bekerjaya, baru berkahwin dan baru juga bercerai. Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Jalinan percintaan mereka juga direstui ibu bapa mereka, cuma Nizam terpaksa menangguhkan perkahwinan mereka sekurang-kurangnya 3 tahun kerana melanjutkan pelajaran keluar negara. Hani yang baik sahsiahnya dan berbudi pekerti, pandai mengemas rumah tangga memahaminya dan sanggup menunggu. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Selain majlis telah siap, tetamu juga telah dijemput, tiba-tiba sehari sebelum majlis berlangsung, Nizam meminta majlis dibatalkan dengan alasan dia telah berkahwin 5 bulan lalu. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Mizan agak terkejut dan tidak bersetuju walau pun dirayu demi menutup maruah keluarga. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Majlis perkahwinan Mizan dan Hani serta jamuan berjalan lancar. Di sebelah petangnya. Nizam dan isterinya, Shela juga tiba dan mereka dijangka akan tinggal di situ beberapa ketika.

Hubungan Nizam dan Mizan tidak mesra sangat. ibu bapa mereka juga memelihara Hani, sebagai adik angkat. Kini, Hani seorang gadis, selain sangat disayangi ibu bapa mereka, Mizan pula mencintainya. Di hari ketibaan Nizam pulang, ibu bapanya telah menetapkan sebagai hari perkahwinan Nizam dan Hani. Di hari itu, Mizan juga pulang sebagai meraikan majlis adiknya, lalu ibu bapanya mencadangkan Mizan menggantikan tempat Nizam. Sementara itu Hani amat berduka, tetapi sebelah malamnya Hani berubah hati semata-mata demi maruah keluarga lalu merayu beberapa kali kepada Mizan mengambilnya sebagai isteri. Mizan bukan sahaja menolak permintaan Hani, sebaliknya mencerca Hani yang dianggap tidak malu. Hani pula terus berdoa. Di awal pagi hari majlis, Mizan berubah hati dan bersetuju. Disebabkan Aidil sudah beritahu kedua-dua keluarga yang mereka akan ke UK, Encik Ismail dna Puan Ainon datang melawat anak mereka sebelum berangkat ke UK. Setibanya Ain dan Aidil di lapangan terbang, Ain terkejut apabila Aidil memberitahu yang dia tidak perlu ikut sama. Dia harus tinggal di KL, pindah keluar daripada rumahnya, jangan hubungi keluarga dan jangan beritahu sesiapa pun dia tidak mengikut Aidil ke UK.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep02
programme.desc: Mizan telah berkahwin dengan Hani, tetapi hubungan mereka sebagai suami isteri tidak berlaku seperti lazim. Mizan selain tidak tidur dan bersentuhan dengan Hani, perbualan mereka pun tentang hal yang penting sahaja, malahan Mizan telah menegaskan lambat laun nanti mereka akan berpisah dengan haluan masingmasing. programme.title: Kembara S4 Ep04
programme.desc: Bersama Hos, Shahrul Kamal membawa penonton mengembara dan mencuba pelbagai aktiviti luar di Mini Amazon Kampung Beng, Lenggong, Perak.

programme.title: Rambo Last Blood
programme.desc: John Rambo, setelah melawan iblisnya selama puluhan tahun, kini hidup dalam kedamaian di peternakan keluarganya di Arizona. Namun, ketenangannya terganggu ketika Gabriela, cucu dari pembantu rumahnya Mara, menghilang setelah menyeberangi perbatasan ke Meksiko untuk bertemu dengan ayah kandungnya. Rambo, yang telah menjadi figur ayah yang sejati bagi Gabriela selama bertahun-tahun, memulai perjalanan yang putus asa dan berbahaya untuk menemukannya.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Uzair dan Madi adalah musuh sekolah. Apabila Madi menghina kawannya Suresh, Uzair menyerang Madi. Madi membalas dengan menyerang rakan-rakan Uzair. Pidottrauma dengan serangan Madi tetapi Uzair cuba untuk menenangkan keadaan. Namun, apabila Madi menyedari bahawa CIkgu Sofi mempunyai sifatlemah lembut terhadap Uzair, Madi menyerang dan menyakiti Cikgu Sofi.

programme.title: Wangi
programme.desc: Nor dan suaminya, Khuzairi tinggal di sebuah banglo bersama dua anak mereka. Selepas melahirkan anak kedua, Nor pulang ke rumah dan ibunya datang untuk menjaganya. Dia perasan bahawa pembantu rumahnya, Bella telah hilang. Bella seperti adik kepada Nor dan dia tinggal bersama mereka. Suaminya mengatakan bahawa Bella telah kembali ke Amsterdam untuk berkahwin. Nor mengesyaki dan tidak lama kemudian anak-anaknya mula mempunyai kelakuan luar biasa. Anak pertama mereka suka bercakap dengan dirinya sendiri dan tidur di tempat yang rawak; suaminya menyembunyikan rahsia manakala seorang wanita tua sentiasa memberi amaran kepada Nor. Tanpa disedari oleh Nor, Bella yang hilang mungkin sedang mengintai di sudut gelap banglo itu.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep 19 Ep19
programme.desc: Shamsul menghantar gambar bapa tirinya Kamal bersama Salina kepada emaknya. Kamal memujuk isterinya sebenarnya Salina adalah rakan niaga dan bukan kekasihnya. Farish masih tidak percaya dengan Kamal. Ryan pula menjadi bodyguard kepada Dato Dahalan, kekasih Dato Dahalan bernama Fazura. Ryan diminta menyiasat kegiatan Fazura selepas diberi wang sebanyak RM 200,00. Ryan mendapati Fazura menggunakan wang tersebut untuk mendapatkan semula hutang anak Dato Dahalan dengannya. Dalam kes berasingan, Taufik memberi amaran kepada Sarrah. Dia akan mencederakannya selepas Sarrah memutuskan hubungan mereka. Untuk keselamatan, Bakri akan terus menjaga Sarrah. Taufik telah membawa rakannya untuk memukul Bakri.

programme.title: Bodyguard Ep 20 Ep20
programme.desc: Shamsul masih syak bapa tirinya Kamal bukan lelaki yang baik, Farish menasihat agar menerima kehidupan bapa tiri seadanya. Salina pula didapati bukan kekasih Kamal, dia sebenarnya gadis suruhan (call girl) untuk melayani klien Kamal. dalam perniagaannya. Ryan rakan sekampung Salina menasihatnya supaya berhenti melakukan pekerjaan tersebut. Shamsul pula cuba ditembak oleh seseorang semasa bersama-sama dengan Farish. Shamsul syak Kamal yang merancang pembunuhan tersebut kerana dia anak tunggal dalam keluarganya. Kematiannya akan memboleh Kamal menguasai harta keluarganya. Siasatan oleh Farish mendapati Pak Long Shamsul yang merancangpembunuhan tersebut. Bakri, bodyguard kepada Sarrah mendapati mereka diekori oleh Taufik. Berlaku pergaduhan yang akhirnya Taufik tertangkap.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit Ep 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Kisah bermula pada satu malam apabila SARAKIT mengalami mimpi yang menakutkan. Dalam mimpinya itu, satu LEMBAGA PEREMPUAN yang berlumuran dengan darah muncul di hadapan SARAKIT sambil meminta tolong. SARAKIT menghampiri LEMBAGA tersebut. Tiba-tiba LEMBAGA itu bertukar wajah menjadi perempuan yang berwajah hodoh dan menakutkan. LEMBAGA itu mengejar SARAKIT. SARAKIT tersedar dari tidurnya apabila dia dikejutkan oleh RAFIQ. Dalam waktu yang sama, bomoh yang diupah oleh PN MARIAM sedang berusaha untuk memisahkan antara SARAKIT dengan RAFIQ. Bomoh itu berpuas hati setelah usahanya selesai.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit Ep 2 Ep2
programme.desc: Sarakit dirogol empat lelaki bertopeng sementara seorang lagi, Ramdi, diminta menjaga di luar rumah. Keesokan hari, ibu bapa Sarakit pergi menjenguk Sarakit dan mendapati rumahnya berkunci dan tiada respon dari Sarakit. Mereka terserempak dengan Pak Bado yang mengadu bahawa Sarakit sudah sombong setelah berkahwin dengan Rafiq dan melanggar adat resam kampung. Sarakit yang sangat lemah dan tidak berdaya untuk bangun dan bersuara mendengar perbualan mereka. Sementara itu, Mariam masih enggan membenarkan Rafiq pulang ke Sarakit atas alasan dia sakit dan cuba mendekatkan Rafiq dengan Dina, bekas teman wanitanya. Pada masa yang sama, Ramdi sering diganggu oleh lembaga putih berambut panjang yang setiap malam merayau-rayau di kampung sambil menangis dan memohon maaf. Pada satu malam, Kiol, salah seorang yang merogol Sarakit, dicekik lembaga putih berambut panjang dan mayatnya dijumpai di sungai dengan jari kelingkingnya dipotong.

programme.desc: Kesilapannya mungkin menyebabkan dia dipenjara, tetapi bagi Firman, ia juga menjadi pemangkin permulaan baru dalam hidup. Trisya seorang gadis yang mendambakan untuk dicintai, tetapi apabila bertemu dengannya barulah dia sedar bahawa cinta sejati bukanlah hamparan bunga mawar. Freez adalah seorang lelaki yang riang yang hanya berfikir tentang melepak dengan rakan-rakannya dan menjadi gembira, manakala Lara adalah seorang yang bersemangat bebas yang mahu membuat jalannya di dunia sendiri. Mereka berempat bertemu di Wira Cinta, sebuah kelab yang dimiliki oleh Kak Pora di mana mereka semua belajar seni mempertahankan diri dan juga mengenali diri mereka sendiri, apabila Pinto, abang ipar Firman dari masa lalunya yang kelam muncul di kelab itu dan menuntut bahawa Firman kembali kepada kumpulan itu atau menghadapi akibatnya.

Kebenaran ternyata lebih mengancam apabila roh yang menghantui tempat itu terbukti benar dan mula menyerang mereka.

programme.desc: Sekumpulan anak muda yang menyukai motor berkuasa tinggi dan suka mengembara merentas desa. Nama kumpulan mereka ialah Rentaz. Ketika berkonvoi ke Betong Siam, mereka dibawa ke alam bawah tanah atau halusinasi dalam koma.

programme.title: 71: Into The Fire
programme.desc: Pada Ogos 1950, menunggu tentera PBB tiba, tentera Korea Selatan berhimpun untuk melindungi Sungai Nakdong. Hanya 71 pelajar-askar yang ditinggalkan untuk mengawal bandar Pohang. Kini mereka dalam misi mempertahankan negara daripada tentera Korea Utara.

programme.title: Khurafat
programme.desc: Kisah bermula dengan Johan, seorang pemuda yang bekerja sebagai Pembantu Hospital. Sudah berkahwin dan mempunyai seorang isteri bernama Aishah. Pasangan ini diawal perkahwinan hidup aman dan bahagia namun tanpa disangka trauma melanda dipertangahan jalan. Mereka sering diganggu oleh lembaga aneh

programme.title: Ghost Writer 2
programme.desc: Kejayaan novel keduanya mengharumkan nama Naya. Malangnya dia lebih dilabelkan sebagai psikik daripada penulis. Ini membuatkan Naya geram dan berat hati untuk berhadapan dengan dunia berhantu itu semula. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila bakal suaminya Vino meninggal dunia secara tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep 5 Ep5
programme.desc: Ashikin membantu Uzair melarikan diri daripada Imran tetapi menerima akibatnya. Uzair tertarik dengan Noramina. Imran kecewa kerana Madi belum sedar daripada koma. Janice berputus asa dengan Ashikin. Perlawanan yang telah diatur dari mula, Uzair kalah dalam perlawanan timbal balik kepada Hatta. Imran perlu berunding tentang perebutan kawasan dengan seorang lelaki misteri bernama Along.

programme.title: Azem 3
programme.desc: Seorang isteri cemburu "zehra" meragui suaminya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan rakannya, dia merancang untuk melaksanakan sihir hitam oleh beberapa syeikh yang jahat untuk mendapatkan suaminya kembali daripada pesaingnya. Beberapa siri peristiwa hebat mula berlaku kepada rakannya berakhir dengan pembunuhan "zehra" y suaminya untuk mengelakkan skandal curang.

programme.title: Balun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang pemuda, Hassan yang membuat keputusan untuk pulang dan menetap di kampung asalnya di Kampung Putra, Kamunting kerana ada beberapa persoalan dan perkara yang harus diselesaikan, di mana salah satu perkaranya adalah perihal tanah milik arwah ayahnya, Mustafa yang dicagarkan pada Orang Kaya Seman sebelum itu.

programme.title: The Cave

programme.title: Takut Ke Tak
programme.desc: Lima pelajar jurusan filem merancang untuk melakukan penggambaran di sebuah rumah berhantu, namun satu demi satu kejadian yang sama seperti kebanyakan filem seram berlaku kepada mereka lalu mereka perlu membuat keputusan penting takut ke tak?

programme.title: Rien Pembunuh Berantai
programme.desc: Rein, seorang lelaki muda dengan masa lalu yang kelam, adalah pelaku kepada mangsa yang dicacatkan yang ditemui di dalam beg pakaian. Dia bekerja di sebuah syarikat swasta dan disenangi ramai orang, tetapi masa lalunya yang kelam membuatkan dia trauma. Dia dibuli oleh kawan-kawannya, ibunya mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan lelaki lain, dan gadis yang dia cintai mengkhianati lelaki lain. Suatu hari, Rein dikehendaki polis dan kini menjadi buruan polis.

programme.title: Jerangkung Dalam Almari
programme.desc: Kehidupan Fikri tidak tenang kerana dia sering diganggu oleh penampakan yang muncul dari almari, mengancam isteri dan anaknya. Berbekalkan ajaran Pak Hassan, Fikri pulang ke rumah lamanya tetapi dia terpaksa berdepan dengan abangnya Ali, yang menyembunyikan rahsia gelap misteri di sebalik ancaman Makhluk di dalam almari.

programme.title: Mat Moto
programme.desc: Filem ini mengikuti perjalanan rakan-rakan "mat moto", juga dikenali sebagai penunggang motosikal, yang berkongsi minat yang sama dalam sukan permotoran. Dalam perjalanan merentasi Malaysia, penunggang motosikal menemui erti persahabatan yang sebenar dan kegembiraan berkongsi hobi yang sama.

programme.title: Janet: Sumpahan Terlarang
programme.desc: Julia adalah gadis Sarawak yang pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk merancang perkahwinannya Farid. Tetapi dia secara tidak sedar menggunakan jepit rambut milik Janet, yang telah menjadi korban ritual dalam membina jambatan.

programme.desc: DAWAMI yang mempunyai kepakaran dalam dunia perubatan tradisional cuba memulihkan keadaan dan menasihati HALIM secara inderect tetapi HALIM tidak mengacuhkan. Freez adalah seorang lelaki yang riang yang hanya berfikir tentang melepak dengan rakan-rakannya dan menjadi gembira, manakala Lara adalah seorang yang bersemangat bebas yang mahu membuat jalannya di dunia sendiri. Mereka berempat bertemu di Wira Cinta, sebuah kelab yang dimiliki oleh Kak Pora di mana mereka semua belajar seni mempertahankan diri dan juga mengenali diri mereka sendiri, apabila Pinto, abang ipar Firman dari masa lalunya yang kelam muncul di kelab itu dan menuntut bahawa Firman kembali kepada kumpulan itu atau menghadapi akibatnya.

programme.title: Anak Jantan
programme.desc: Darin dihantui oleh kehidupan yang lalu. Gaya hidup negatifnya berubah sama sekali apabila beliau jatuh cinta kepada seorang wanita dari kampungnya bernama Nara. Tidak lama kemudian, pasangan ini berhijrah ke bandar KL untuk memulakan kehidupan baru. Mereka dikurniakan seorang anak lelaki yang bijak bernama Saufi. Malangnya, kebahagiaan keluarga mereka tidak bertahan lama dengan ketibaan Somchai, seorang rakan lama yang kembali menyebabkan pergolakan di tempat kerja Darin.

programme.title: Janet: Sumpahan Terlarang
programme.desc: Julia adalah gadis Sarawak yang pergi ke Kuala Lumpur untuk merancang perkahwinannya Farid. Tetapi dia secara tidak sedar menggunakan jepit rambut milik Janet, yang telah menjadi korban ritual dalam membina jambatan.

programme.title: Siapa Tak Sayang Bini 2
programme.desc: Merupakan lanjutan daripada kisah dua keluarga yang ingin mengawal pasangan masing-masing. Kisah kali ini bermula apabila Saiful ternampak Karim yang sudah tidak takut isteri berjalan dengan seorang wanita muda bernama Sephia. Karim sering mendengar luahan Sephia yang sedang bergaduh dengan teman lelakinya. Saiful yang suka menyibuk itu memberitahu perkara tersebut kepada Kasmah, isteri Karim. Pelbagai kekalutan berlaku setelah Kasmah mengesyaki suaminya berlaku curang dan meminta bantuan Kamisah untuk menyiasat perkara ini. Dalam masa yang sama, Karim dengan bantuan Kassim mencari jalan untuk menjernihkan keadaan.

programme.title: Rentak Desa
programme.desc: Pencemaran alam menyebabkan penduduk kampung mula menunjuk perasaan. Mat Desa dan Wairah seringkali berasa bahawa penduduk di situ hanya hidup atas empati pemaju. Hanya kerana ingin membuat jalan raya, bukit dan pokok ditebang manakala sungai dicemari sisa bahan toksik - menyebabkan ikan mati dan beracun. Sebuah penemuan merungkai segalanya.

programme.title: Yang Berhormat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kuping, anak gelandangan yang menjalani kehidupan di Kuala Lumpur dengan melakukan pelbagai pekerjaan. Dia bersahabat dengan seorang OKU bernama Lobak dan Mat Yee. Pada suatu hari, Kuping terserempak dengan seorang lelaki bernama YB Salleh Ali dan terpesona melihat beliau memberi ceramah politik. Kuping yang terinspirasi dengan YB Salleh Ali itu ingin membantu Lobak untuk memikat seorang gadis bernama Mastura.

programme.title: Estet
programme.desc: Mengisahkan para pekerja estet Cinta Manis yang bakal bertarung dengan kumpulan estet Red Cobra dalam satu perlawanan bola sepak yang sudah 20 tahun tidak diadakan. Farid dan Shashi, dua pekerja estet yang berkawan sejak kecil, menjadi harapan pekerja estet yang lain untuk menyelamatkan penindasan yang dilakukan oleh kerani estet, Pooniah. Seorang gadis cantik bernama Geetha tertarik hati dengan Farid dan Shashi. Sesi latihan dikendalikan oleh Subramaniam iaitu bapa Geetha yang dilantik sebagai jurulatih. Ayah kepada Shashi, Apaa, adalah pemain bola yang sangat mahir, tetapi telah berlaku insiden semasa perlawanan bola sepak estet itu dahulu yang mana kakinya patah diterjah oleh Junna, seorang samseng estet yang sengaja ingin menamatkan karier Apaa atas upahan Pooniah 20 tahun yang lalu. Berjayakah Farid dan Shashi serta kawan-kawannya membebaskan pekerja estet Cinta Manis daripada penindasan Pooniah?

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Unleashed
programme.desc: Fok Kit is the hottest underground boxer with unbeatable records. To save their boxing studio from being sold, he must win the fight against Shaolin who is known as "Killing Machine". Fok Kit is defeated and badly hurt in the fight, which is a set-up by Lok, who wants to take revenge on Fok Kits master, Debo.

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: Shadows
programme.desc: Ching is a forensic psychiatrist who has the power to enter a persons subconscious mind. In her latest case, she suspects that another psychiatrist is responsible for a brutal murder-cum-suicide case involving a social worker. In the investigation process, Ching finds herself under suspicion instead, as she comes face-to-face with a past trauma

programme.title: God of Gambler's Return
programme.desc: The God of Gamblers, Gao Jin, quits gambling and live a quiet life with his wife. However, a Taiwanese crime boss wants to become the new God of Gamblers and get rid of him, so he kills Gao Jins pregnant wife to force him to the casino table. Gao Jin is indignant and vows to fight the crime boss to avenge his wifes death.

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: Septet: The Story of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: Ghost Wedding
programme.desc: Photographer Zhi Cheng is entangled with a "woman in red", leading to the deaths of his relatives one by one. When the girl he likes, Si Tong, also dies mysteriously, Zhi Cheng vows to find out the truth but ends up revealing the secret of a "ghost marriage"...

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Keep Rolling
programme.desc: Directorial debut of Man Lim Chung, who spent 3 years filming this documentary about the life and filmmaking philosophy of Ann Hui, one of Hong Kongs greatest filmmakers. It traces Huis life story and her 40-year careers ups and downs using film footages, candid conversations with Hui, and interviews with her collaborators, family and friends.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: An accomplished police officer, Mann has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, he is forced to perform when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector, who is suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: L Storm
programme.desc: ICAC officer Luk and Chief Inspector Lau both hit a dead end when investigating their respective bribery and money laundering cases. When Luk is accused of bribery after being framed by the money launderers, he risks everything he has to find crucial evidence against them to clear his name.

programme.title: Two Tigers
programme.desc: This crime comedy is about a bumbling young man Fang Nan, who kidnaps a middle-aged businessman Zhang Cheng Gong for ransom. However, the captor becomes the captive when Zhang turns the tables on Fang and forces him to complete three tasks. The two men soon find themselves sharing a journey filled with absurdity and deception.

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: Over My Dead Body
programme.desc: This dark comedy begins with an unidentified corpse appearing at the doorstep of a residential flat. Fearing that the corpse will turn their flats into "haunted flats", which will cause a drastic drop in the property value, the four families living on the same floor attempt to move the corpse away, embroiling themselves in chaos.

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Tales from the Occult: Body and Soul
programme.desc: This horror anthology series returns to feature three spooky crime stories about an ex-hair model, a cat lover and the love triangle between a dental nurse, a dentist and a chef. The stories depict their paths from obsession to madness, eventually tipping them over to the dark side of human nature.

Chow Mo Wan encounters many women in his life but is touched by none after he lost his true love. Following an encounter one day, he decides to write a fiction titled 2046 which takes place at Room 2046. Nothing ever changes at Room 2046, and people go there to find their lost memories.

programme.title: MMA Diva
programme.desc: Xin Lan takes over her fathers MMA club which is heavily in debt due to poor business. After He Hua defeated Xin Lan, she replaces her to become the new top MMA Diva and challenges Xin Lans MMA club to a duel. As Xin Lan is injured, she seeks help from a retried MMA superstar to fight the battle on her behalf to reclaim the clubs and her honour.

programme.title: The Macaque Monkey
programme.desc: The world is in chaos after the tree of life was burnt. Sun Wu Kong decides to return to the past to resurrect it, but his divine power is unstable after losing the golden hoop, and he must find his younger self to team up to find the power of time. As the six-eared Macaque Monkey also wants the power of time, they clash in a fierce battle

programme.title: Divergence
programme.desc: Three men are going beyond what their jobs require them to do. An ill-fated police detective runs into a woman during his investigation on a money laundering case, a lawyer protects a corrupt businessman from law and a ruthless killer violates his code to get involved in a police investigation. These three men are thrown together by circumstance...

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: I Corrupt All Cops
programme.desc: Corruption was rampant in the Hong Kong Police Force in 1960s and 70s. Chief Inspector Lak launders drug money with three other police officers, and a young officer from the newly established Independent Commission Against Corruption division is determined to bring them down.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon II: Wild Wild Bunch
programme.desc: Starring four Hong Kong Film Awards Best Actors, Simon Yam, Louis Koo, Tony Leung Ka Fai and Gordon Lam, this action-thriller follows the real-life kidnapping events that terrorized Hong Kongs elite in the 1990s by serial billionaire-kidnapper Logan and his gang.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together with her half-sister and her nine-year-old son, the newly reunited family come together to support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Peng and Mang have nothing in common but spend a magical night in Rome together. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: Wu Xia
programme.desc: Martial artist Liu hides his identity and lives in a remote village with his wife Ah Yu and their two sons, but somehow gets embroiled in a bizarre murder case. Constable Xu is a kung fu fanatic, whose curiosity forces Liu into a death duel with the Sect Leader of the 72 Demons, and puts Lius family and homeland in a great danger...

programme.title: The Emperor and his Brother
programme.desc: The Emperor Qianlong is not the legitimate successor to the throne at birth, but he only learns the truth when two senior members of a subversive anti-government secret organisation contact him years later. As it happens, the chef of this organisation is Qianlongs younger brother and they must now confront each other in opposing roles

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: Holy Flame of the Martial World
programme.desc: This internationally popular tale of a brother and sister, seeking vengeance for the death of their parents through using the mythical yin/yang Holy Flame kung-fu technique. It's an outstanding epic choreographed and co-starring lead "Venom" Kuo Chue (aka. Philip Kwok).

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: The Spirit of the Sword
programme.desc: Water Clan Chief is severely wounded by a samurai killer shortly before the annual duel at Tai Lake. He sends his brother Bao Yu on a long journey to find an antidote for him. On the way, Bao Yu encounters Little Princess and falls in love with her, not knowing that she is hiding a secret plot

programme.title: The Adventures of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his peoples livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: The Deadly Duo
programme.desc: The prince of the Sung Dynasty is captured by the Chin invaders and is guarded by top martial arts masters. It is up to two powerful patriots to fight the overwhelming odds and pull off the impossible: to rescue the royal Prince and get out of the Chin stronghold alive.

programme.title: When the Clouds Roll By
programme.desc: Su is a schizophrenic who refuses to believe that her pilot lover is killed in a plane crash and makes up stories to deal with things. She runs into an old classmate Lai, who is also a doctor one day, and he finds ways to treat her illness. Su slowly recovers and accepts the reality, as well as her newfound love.

programme.title: The Daredevils
programme.desc: Corrupt general Wang Li assumes power by killing his superior. The son of the murdered superior befriends four street performers called The Venoms, and they help him take revenge by posing as government officials offering a peace token to the corrupt general. When Wang arrives at a warehouse, he is ambushed by the Venoms!

programme.title: Sweet And Wild
programme.desc: Fang is a spunky young village girl who is not afraid to fight back against hooligans. She gets into trouble with the biggest hoodlum Tong when she foils his plans with a maid, causing Tong to plot a revenge. Luckily a man whom she is attracted to, Hai, comes in time to her rescue. Can they fight back?

programme.title: Tragic Commitment
programme.desc: When the husband of a doctor, Tung is fatally wounded in an accident, he reveals to her about his affair with Blackie, who is impregnated with his baby. Despite the devastation of the betrayal and the eventual death of her husband, Tung is pressured by her mother-in-law into putting up with Blackie and offer $1M for her baby...

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: The Bride from Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: Return of the One-armed Swordsman
programme.desc: One-armed Swordsman Fang Kang wants to lead a quiet life with his wife, but when she is abducted by the Eight Demon Swordsmen clan, he is forced to take them on in order to save her.

programme.title: Hong Kong Rhapsody
programme.desc: Hong Kong rhapsody is a musical extravaganza full of song and dance! Peter Chen-Ho stars as a playboy magician who changes his ways after he becomes the guardian of a young singer (Li Ching), the daughter of a deceased magician friend.

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their masters birthday.

programme.title: Beyond the Great Wall
programme.desc: Wang Zhao Jun refuses to bribe the imperial painter, so he draws an ugly portrait of her, preventing her from being selected by the Emperor until they meet in person. The painter ends up in exile and plots for Wang to marry the Huns warlord as a revenge. The Emperor rejects this, provoking a war which is only averted when Wang sacrifices herself.

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao. Meanwhile, a royal treasure is stolen while a murder takes place. Bao is ordered to solve the case in ten days and Zhan quickly sets off to investigate. Will they solve the case in time?

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: The Fastest Sword
programme.desc: Southern Swordsman Ting is named The Fastest Sword but is defeated by a street monk and has to fulfil his promise of working on stone craving with the monk for three years. Ting returns home to lead a peaceful life after that and declines all fight challenges. Even so, he is forced to fight the Northern Swordsman. Who will win finally?

programme.title: Blue Skies
programme.desc: A young singer Hsiao Yun becomes an overnight sensation after standing in for another singer at the eleventh hour. Her success comes at a heavy price however, when her love with a pianist suffers. On top of this, Hsiao Yun must also deal with the unwanted affections from an influential backer of her show.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his bride use the deadly weapon - Phoenix Lute to fight against evil, but the lute accidentally falls into the hands of bandits hoping to use it to take control of the province. Gui Wu must now fight to recover the lute and beat the bandits.

programme.title: Illicit Desire
programme.desc: This instant cult classic adapts three erotic and mystical tales from the Chinese classical works, with stories spanning across time from the Tang to Ming dynasties. The stories, filled with characters such as emperors, concubines, monks and fortune-tellers, intertwine in a world of adultery, lust and greed, alongside great costumes!

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Shaolin Rescuers
programme.desc: Hong Xi Guan of Shaolin is chased and wounded by a martial arts scum who took refuge in the Qing court. He is saved and healed by friends from the wet market and they hide Hong in a bean curd shop to protect him. However, Hongs enemy finds him and ambushes him at the shop, hoping to capture Hong and all his friends.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: The Golden Seal
programme.desc: Dai Tian Chou practices martial arts since young so he can avenge his fathers death. He meets Wu Xiao Yan who is disguised as a man one day and is suddenly beaten by a group of gangsters. Wu begs her father to allow her to take Dai back home to recover. Little does Dai know this is his chance to take revenge.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: House of Traps
programme.desc: It all started with THE FIVE VENOMS, the internationally loved kung-fu thriller which introduced director Chang Cheh's recurring cast of martial arts masters. It continued through more than a dozen high-flying, bloody good entertainments featuring the same action actors in pairs, trios, quartets, and, most memorably, quintets. While this is considered the last official "Venoms" movie, what a film it is. The title does not lie: an evil prince has secreted stolen imperial treasures in a building that practically bristles with booby-trapped blades. Bodies are pierced, limbs are cut off, and there's one plasma-spurting attack after another as heroes and rogues alike try to solve the secrets of the hell house. The core Venoms themselves choreograph the gory fun in this fond farewell to their worldwide film series sensation.

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Return to the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: The second film of the trilogy, Gordon Liu plays Zhou Ren Jie, a man who impersonates a monk in order to learn kung fu in Shaolin, and eventually creates his own Shaolin style of scaffolding kung fu.

programme.title: Dawn will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: Brotherhood
programme.desc: Liu serves his triad society loyally and tries to live a respectable life, but over time his good intentions lead him to an all-out gang war with a startling conclusion.

programme.desc: The Yarn Fairy / Bake It Til You Make It - When the trees start losing their leaves, Phoebe begins knitting the trees in the park sweaters, but when the neighborhood kids see the sweaters they think they're a mysterious "Yarn Fairy," and they want to see her in action, making it much harder for the Dews to put more sweaters on the latest trees that have lost their leaves. / When Marcus and Harper team-up for a school project, they decide to bake something ("It's like inventing, but with food!"), only to come across multiple baking misshaps (and happy accidents) along the way that the Dew Drops must secretly assist them with.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep10
